PIZARRO;
A
TRAGEDY,
IN FIVE ACTS;
AS PERFORMED AT THE THEATRE ROYAL IN
<HI>Drury-Lane:</HI>
TAKEN FROM THE GERMAN DRAMA OF
<HI>KOTZEBUE;</HI>
AND
ADAPTED TO THE ENGLISH STAGE
BY
RICHARD BRINSLEY SHERIDAN.</P>
<P>DUBLIN:
PRINTED FOR J. MOORE, 45, COLLEGE-GREEN.</P>
<P>1799.</P>
